# Dependencies to Add to build.gradle.kts

## Add to plugins block:
```kotlin
plugins {
    id("com.android.application")
    id("org.jetbrains.kotlin.android")
    id("kotlin-kapt")
    id("org.jetbrains.kotlin.plugin.serialization") version "1.9.0"  // ‚Üê ADD THIS LINE
}
```

## Add to dependencies block:
```kotlin
dependencies {
    // ... existing dependencies ...
    
    // ========== P2P SYNC DEPENDENCIES ==========
    
    // Ed25519 Cryptography for message signing
    implementation("net.i2p.crypto:eddsa:0.3.0")
    
    // JSON Serialization for sync messages
    implementation("org.jetbrains.kotlinx:kotlinx-serialization-json:1.6.0")
    
    // OPTIONAL: I2P Networking (can add later in Phase 3)
    // implementation("net.i2p.android:client:0.9.50")
    // implementation("net.i2p.android:helper:0.9.50")
    
    // OPTIONAL: QR Code generation for referrals (if not already using)
    // implementation("com.google.zxing:core:3.5.1")
    // implementation("com.journeyapps:zxing-android-embedded:4.3.0")
}
```

## Update AndroidManifest.xml (if using I2P later):
```xml
<manifest>
    <!-- Add permissions -->
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
    
    <!-- Optional: for background sync -->
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE" />
</manifest>
```

## Sync Gradle:
```bash
./gradlew clean
./gradlew build
```
